00085 static wmKeyMapItem *rna_KeyMap_item_new(wmKeyMap *km, ReportList *reports, const char *idname, int type, int value,
00086                                          int any, int shift, int ctrl, int alt, int oskey, int keymodifier)
00087 {
00088 /*  wmWindowManager *wm = CTX_wm_manager(C); */
00089     char idname_bl[OP_MAX_TYPENAME];
00090     int modifier = 0;
00091 
00092     /* only on non-modal maps */
00093     if (km->flag & KEYMAP_MODAL) {
00094         BKE_report(reports, RPT_ERROR, "Not a non-modal keymap");
00095         return NULL;
00096     }
00097 
00098     WM_operator_bl_idname(idname_bl, idname);
00099 
00100     if (shift) modifier |= KM_SHIFT;
00101     if (ctrl) modifier |= KM_CTRL;
00102     if (alt) modifier |= KM_ALT;
00103     if (oskey) modifier |= KM_OSKEY;
00104 
00105     if (any) modifier = KM_ANY;
00106 
00107     return WM_keymap_add_item(km, idname_bl, type, value, modifier, keymodifier);
00108 }

00110 static wmKeyMapItem *rna_KeyMap_item_new_modal(wmKeyMap *km, ReportList *reports, const char *propvalue_str,
00111                                                int type, int value, int any, int shift, int ctrl, int alt,
00112                                                int oskey, int keymodifier)
00113 {
00114     int modifier = 0;
00115     int propvalue = 0;
00116 
00117     /* only modal maps */
00118     if ((km->flag & KEYMAP_MODAL) == 0) {
00119         BKE_report(reports, RPT_ERROR, "Not a modal keymap");
00120         return NULL;
00121     }
00122 
00123     if (shift) modifier |= KM_SHIFT;
00124     if (ctrl) modifier |= KM_CTRL;
00125     if (alt) modifier |= KM_ALT;
00126     if (oskey) modifier |= KM_OSKEY;
00127 
00128     if (any) modifier = KM_ANY;
00129 
00130     /* not initialized yet, do delayed lookup */
00131     if (!km->modal_items)
00132         return WM_modalkeymap_add_item_str(km, type, value, modifier, keymodifier, propvalue_str);
00133 
00134     if (RNA_enum_value_from_id(km->modal_items, propvalue_str, &propvalue) == 0)
00135         BKE_report(reports, RPT_WARNING, "Property value not in enumeration");
00136 
00137     return WM_modalkeymap_add_item(km, type, value, modifier, keymodifier, propvalue);
00138 }

00171 static void rna_generic_op_invoke(FunctionRNA *func, int flag)
00172 {
00173     PropertyRNA *parm;
00174 
00175     RNA_def_function_flag(func, FUNC_NO_SELF|FUNC_USE_CONTEXT);
00176     parm = RNA_def_pointer(func, "operator", "Operator", "", "Operator to call");
00177     RNA_def_property_flag(parm, PROP_REQUIRED);
00178 
00179     if (flag & WM_GEN_INVOKE_EVENT) {
00180         parm = RNA_def_pointer(func, "event", "Event", "", "Event");
00181         RNA_def_property_flag(parm, PROP_REQUIRED);
00182     }
00183 
00184     if (flag & WM_GEN_INVOKE_SIZE) {
00185         RNA_def_int(func, "width", 300, 0, INT_MAX, "", "Width of the popup", 0, INT_MAX);
00186         RNA_def_int(func, "height", 20, 0, INT_MAX, "", "Height of the popup", 0, INT_MAX);
00187     }
00188 
00189     if (flag & WM_GEN_INVOKE_RETURN) {
00190         parm = RNA_def_enum_flag(func, "result", operator_return_items, OPERATOR_CANCELLED, "result", "");
00191         RNA_def_function_return(func, parm);
00192     }
00193 }
